      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new? This beauty is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered its whole life, and you won\u2019t find a single scratch or dent anywhere. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy this gem. Come check it out and see for yourself why I\u2019m so in love with it!",
