    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54B32 high-pressure die-cast iron block engine with individual throttle bodies. This specimen has undergone a comprehensive preventative maintenance suite, including a dual-VANOS overhaul and a reinforced rear subframe carrier panel to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise gate engagement, paired with a factory variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Suspension kinematics are preserved via refreshed bushings and OEM dampers, maintaining the chassis's legendary neutral balance. With documented valve clearances and flawless compression across all six cylinders, this is a mechanically superlative example for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
