      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car is in absolute showroom condition, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment and never driven in inclement weather. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with zero stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of perfection; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, devoid of any creasing or wear, and still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a spotless engine bay and a full documented service history performed exclusively by master technicians at the original dealership. This is a rare opportunity to own a factory-fresh example that satisfies the most demanding standards of a serious collector. Includes all original keys, window stickers, and manuals.",
